    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dyeing cloth by repeatedly putting a resist on different parts of its pattern and placing it in successive dye baths.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
